<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #FF9800; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background-color: #FF9800; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    .info-box { background-color: #fff3e0; border-left: 4px solid #FF9800; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .important { background-color: #ffebee; border-left: 4px solid #f44336; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Administrator Invitation</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>

      <p>
        You have been invited to be an <strong>Administrator</strong> for <strong><%= @account.name %></strong> on KaryaApp.
      </p>

      <div class="important">
        <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> As an administrator, you will have full access to manage this account,
        including the ability to invite other administrators, managers, and users.
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <strong>Account:</strong> <%= @account.name %><br/>
        <strong>Your Role:</strong> Administrator<br/>
        <strong>Invitation expires:</strong> <%= @expires_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>
      </div>

      <p><strong>As an Administrator, you can:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Invite and manage managers and users</li>
        <li>Manage account settings</li>
        <li>View and manage all tasks</li>
        <li>Full administrative access to the account</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Click the button below to accept the invitation and create your administrator account:</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= @signup_url %>" class="button">Accept Admin Invitation</a>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">
        Or copy and paste this link into your browser:<br/>
        <%= @signup_url %>
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        This invitation will expire in <%= UserInvitation::TOKEN_EXPIRY_DAYS %> days.
        If you didn't expect this invitation or have questions, please contact the person who sent this invitation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from KaryaApp. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
